  <description>
  Object Ledge is a platform for building applications in Java 2 Standard and Enterprise Edition 
  environments. ObjectLedge follows component / container and Inversion Of Control design paradigms implemented 
  with the excellent PicoContainer (http://picocontainer.org) package. ObjectLedge provides a number of components - 
  basic building blocks of the applications, a few extensions to the Pico framework, customized containers for 
  easy deployment of applications in command line, daemon, and J2EE servlet environments.
  </description>
